<template>
     <el-menu-item index="4" v-if="$store.state.email" @click="logout()">Logout</el-menu-item>
</template>
<script>
export default {
    mounted() {
        this.$store.commit('initialiseStore')
    },
    methods: {
        logout() {
            this.$store.commit('logout')
        }

    },
}

</script>
